The paper discusses automated brain tumor detection and segmentation from MRI of the brain, which is a topic related to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI). Additionally, the paper focuses on medical imaging (cs.Medical Imaging) and the use of neural networks (cs.NEURAL) for brain tumor detection and segmentation.
